Package: pi-relay-control
Version: 1.0.0+202606031456
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: baboonwatch
Installed-Size: 94
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.0), liblgpio1 (>= 0.1.6.1), libstdc++6 (>= 5.2)
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: GPIO Relay Control for Raspberry Pi 5
 Controls a relay via GPIO with socket interface and state persistence.
 Restores last known relay state on startup.
 GPIO pin and port are configurable via /etc/pi-relay-control.conf.
